<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Meato Activation Email</title>
    <style>
        /* base */

        body {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            color: #222222;
        }

        a {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;

        }

        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        /* layouts */

        .email-wrapper {
            min-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .email header {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        /* Button  */
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
  <div class="email-header">
    <h1>Welcome to Meato, Manager!</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="email-body">
    <h3>Hello <%= name %>,</h3>
    <p>
      We're excited to have you join Meato as a manager. To activate your account and begin managing your vendors, please use the following activation code:
    </p>
    <h2><%= otp %></h2>
    <p>
      Enter this code on the manager activation page within the next 5 minutes to complete your onboarding.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you did not sign up for a manager account with Meato, please disregard this email.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="email-footer">
    <p>
      If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to us at
      <a href="mailto:support@xyz.com">support@xyz.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>